{{Infobox journal | cover = | editor = Jason Wyman | discipline = [[Theology]] | abbreviation = Union Semin. Q. Rev. | publisher = [[Union Theological Seminary (Manhattan)|Union Theological Seminary]] | country = | history = 1939-present | frequency = Quarterly | website = http://usqr.utsnyc.edu/ | link1 = http://usqr.utsnyc.edu/?page_id=122 | link1-name = Online access | link2 = http://usqr.utsnyc.edu/?page_id=62 | link2-name = Online archive | ISSN = 0362-1545 | LCCN = 52017050 | OCLC = 781575097 }} The '''''Union Seminary Quarterly Review''''' is a quarterly [[Peer-review|peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] covering [[theology]] that was established in 1939. The [[editor-in-chief]] is Jason Wyman.
